snippet.textDisplay:
Why these beautiful creations lead to a tussle for possession of such art and artists among the citizens of our two nations?

Would we like to call every single talent born on the face of this world as being our nation's citizen?

Why cannot we just appreciate the beauty of these artists and the mesmerizing pieces of music they create? Without thinking of their nationhood?

God decided to get them born at a particular place. None of the nations did anything about it.

So please, relax and enjoy the wonders without throwing nationality into it.
